    <mxCell id="tool2" value="&lt;b&gt;2. Card Selector (LLM)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Trace → Proposal JSON&lt;br&gt;6 output fields only:&lt;br&gt;diagnosis, card_ids,&lt;br&gt;query, rationale,&lt;br&gt;expected_effect, confidence&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;No budget/shell/git/API&lt;/i&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#a5d6a7;strokeColor=#43a047;strokeWidth=1.5;fontSize=9;align=left;spacingLeft=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
